data.description: Welcome to this two-story home nestled in the desirable Pepperhill community in convenient North Charleston. While this charming residence may need a little tender loving care, it offers a world of potential and an ideal canvas for your dream home!As you step inside, you'll immediately appreciate the open floor plan that fills the space with an abundance of natural light. The family room serves as the heart of the home, featuring easy access to the patio and a fenced-in backyard. It's the perfect spot for relaxing, entertaining, or enjoying the beautiful South Carolina weather.This space seamlessly transitions into the dining area and kitchen, where you'll find plenty of cabinet and countertop space. The kitchen also boasts a breakfast bar and a cozy eat-in area.Venturing upstairs, the owner's suite awaits with its tray ceiling, spacious walk-in closet, and an en-suite bath. The en-suite bath features a dual sink vanity, a step-in shower, and a relaxing soaking tub.  The second floor doesn't stop there; it also houses three additional bedrooms, providing plenty of space for family, guests, or even a home office. There is also a full bathroom.  With some TLC and your personal touch, this Pepperhill gem has the potential to become the home of your dreams. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own!  ADT security suite that comes pre-installed with the house. Selling as is. Seller will make no repairs.
